# OPTIONAL: server-side NVIDIA NIM key, used ONLY for background health probes
# (so /models can render without any user logged in). User-facing chat traffic
# always uses the per-user key supplied at registration (BYOK), never this one.
#
# - Leave this file empty / absent: server starts fine, health probes are
#   skipped until at least one user registers (then their key is borrowed
#   transparently for probes).
# - Provide a key: probes use it, the file's perms should be 600.
#
# Get a key: https://build.nvidia.com  (free tier with credits)

NVIDIA_API_KEY=
